headline: Bria Shea named president of Xcel Energy for Minnesota, the Dakotas
summary: Bria Shea has been named president of Xcel Energy for the company’s Minnesota, North Dakota and South Dakota region. Shea, joined Xcel Energy in 2008 and has held several leadership roles on the regulatory team. She most recently was regional vice president for Planning and Policy. In that role Shea led government affairs and regulatory strategy for resource, transmission and distribution ...

headline: Bria Shea named President, Xcel Energy – Minnesota, North and South Dakota
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, October 21, 2025--Xcel Energy today named Bria Shea as president, Xcel Energy – Minnesota, North Dakota and South Dakota, effective immediately.
